<H3> <TI>   Izetbegovic Receives Croatian SDA Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Izetbegovic Receives Croatian SDA Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0106190694 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1700 GMT 1 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0106190694 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Alija Izetbegovic, president of the 
Bosnia-Herzegovina Presidency, today received a delegation of 
the Party of Democratic Action of Croatia headed by party 
chairman [name indistinct]. Stressed in the talks was complete 
congruence of aims and program orientations between the Party of 
Democratic Action of Bosnia-Herzegovina and the Party of 
Democratic Action (?of Croatia). 
  The delegation [words indistinct] informed President 
Izetbegovic of very fruitful contacts with representatives of 
political and religious institutions during its visit to 
Sarajevo. Members of the delegation reiterated their support for 
the policy of the Presidency of Bosnia-Herzegovina and the Party 
of Democratic Action of Bosnia-Herzegovina, particularly as 
regards the realization and implementation of the (?Washington) 
[word indistinct] agreement on the Federation of 
Bosnia-Herzegovina. 

</TEXT>

