  [Excerpt] According to information from the 
surveillance-intelligence unit of the Operative Group East 
Bosnia of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army, the aggressor's units in 
Gorazde are still 300-400 meters from the town center. This 
once again proves that the aggressor is deceiving the domestic 
and international public daily, which requires a more energetic 
action by the UN Security Council and NATO and calls for an 
immediate realization of Resolution No. 913 and the NATO 
ultimatum. Since this morning, the Serbo-Montenegrin fascists 
have been opening fire from antiaircraft machine guns and 
antiaircraft guns at Hrenovica and [word indistinct] and from 
antiaircraft machine guns, [words indistinct] and sniper rifles 
at Djinjici, Stupi, Brijegi, and [word indistinct]. There are 
chetnik infantry arms provocations along the 
Osanica-Ilovaca-Orahovice defense line. [passage omitted] 

