<H3> <TI>   Montenegrins Arrested for Smuggling Oil </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Montenegrins Arrested for Smuggling Oil </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0606082894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
0700 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0606082894 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Albanian authorities have arrested 25 citizens 
of the FRY charged with organized smuggling of oil across Skadar 
Lake. Those arrested belong to a group of Montenegrins from 
Zeta who were shipping oil to Montenegro. The Albanian 
authorities arrested them after supervision of cross-border 
traffic was stepped up in line with UN observers' demands. As 
of Friday Macedonia [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia 
-- FYROM] had also stepped up customs control measures, 
especially concerning fuel. 

</TEXT>

