<F P=103> LD0406102094 </F>
<F P=104>  Budapest Kossuth Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Hungarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] From Monday the publication PESTI HIRLAP 
[center-right daily] will be discontinued. The board of 
trustees of the 150 Years Foundation, the publisher, decided to 
suspend publication of the paper due to the publisher's 
difficult financial situation. The foundation's board of 
trustees, however, is ready to hold talks with its creditors on 
a debt settlement. It is also ready to hold talks with new 
investors on a possible restart or sale of PESTI HIRLAP. 

</TEXT>

