considered the Alliance of Free Democrats [SZDSZ] a necessary 
coalition partner and the Federation of Young Democrats [Fidesz] 
a possible one. This stance has been confirmed by the presidium, 
and today I will submit it to the national executive. [passage 
omitted] The presidium has also confirmed that we propose Gyula 
Horn as the MSZP's nomination for prime minister. 
  [Nagy] So there will be one candidate? 
