name of Laszlo Bekesi [author of the MSZP's economic program] 
had also been raised, as a minority opinion. By the way, we 
invited Laszlo Bekesi to the presidium session. He also outlined 
his views on political and personnel issues. 
  The presidium has confirmed that the MSZP program in 
economic 
as well as in other areas is the program we presented to the 
people during the election campaign, and it is on this program 
that we wish to hold talks with the possible coalition partners. 
[end recording] 

